      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PURE MOMENTUM (1) last appeared when too good (23.13) over 400m at this track on November 18. Resumes after finishing fifth (23.13) at this track over 400m six-and-a-half months ago. Looks a key player drawing the cherry. BLUE BLARNEY (2) jumped from this same draw and was close to the lead throughout before boxing on well and holding a 3.5 lengths third (22.90) at this track over 400m in a Maiden. Has good early burn and drawn to be prominent early off a low draw. Has the ability and can measure up. SKY KING (8) jumps from box 8 again after placing (17.97) last time at Richmond Straight over 324m. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from on outside draw. Can measure up. HEAVENLY SHADOW (4) is in the mix after placing last time out.",
